{"tid":487208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［FBI]支国直播平台小學女生掀衣露體　自誇粉絲多　平台稱已禁未成年人註冊","createTime":"2017-12-02T14:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T15:04:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce9e689536c62c02a30537a4214a84c0658216c","tid":487208,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/221945_d849f54499020fb46275f40402425c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F221945_d849f54499020fb46275f40402425c49.jpg&h=d84459ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地直播平台「美拍」被揭發有小學生等未成年人直播脫衣露體，從網上片段可見，有兒童在直播期間掀起上衣，有直播觀眾留言慫恿主播脫衣。有玩直播的小學生自言，常看到下流的說話，但看多了就不覺憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒訪問到自稱出生於2005年的小學生，她直言裸體直播不是為賺錢，是為了好玩，更稱「我在我們班粉絲最多」。<br />\n<br />\n據「美拍」人員表示，平台設有圖像及封面識別，「現在應該不會讓未成年人新註冊」，亦限制了已有的未成人帳戶直播功能，平台將特別監控。華中師範大學生命科學學院教授彭曉輝指，有關現象對女生成長是個非常嚴重的事件，「她（女生）不明真相」，認為除父母對此有責任外，直播平台應負有最大責任。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171201/s00004/1512103247451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171201%2Fs00004%2F1512103247451&d=Qp05Lx6YjSJ46TstKj3jbfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2503476e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171201%2Fs00004%2F1512103247451&h=289e1522\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171201/s00004/1512103247451</a>"},{"pid":"1309f776e0bf96a87f487b47077e3b77b81b5067","tid":487208,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛點睇支那咁自由開放</strong></span>"},{"pid":"33b3af43e62804e1d1d14acd998fb5456f8057da","tid":487208,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"有冇Backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}